Package: phantomos-k0s
Version: @VERSION@
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: @MAINTAINER@
Installed-Size: @INSTALLED_SIZE@
Depends: python3, bash (>= 4), curl, jq, git, unzip, ca-certificates
Recommends: pciutils, skopeo, docker.io
Homepage: https://github.com/foundationbot/Phantom-OS-KubernetesOptions
Description: PhantomOS bootstrap scripts and manifests for k0s
 Ships the Phantom-OS-KubernetesOptions tree under
 /opt/Phantom-OS-KubernetesOptions so a freshly imaged robot can run
 configure-host.sh and bootstrap-robot.sh to bring up a single-node k0s
 cluster with the PhantomOS workloads.
 .
 The package contains scripts, base/stack manifests, host-config
 templates, and the ArgoCD terraform module. k0s, kubectl, helm and
 terraform themselves are downloaded by bootstrap-robot.sh at run time
 and are not bundled.
